  "body": "<p>Last year there was one theme that outnumbered all the rest. Extremely ornate and beautiful, any twist on Alice and Wonderland was a feast for the eyes. One that I had the pleasure of scrapbooking was \"Erika in Wonderland\". Here are just a few details from the spectacular event.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19a-DSC_0110-600x415.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79b5ad1137ef2268.jpg?v=1782529651\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"19b-DSC_0105-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ffaba5a039bc5703.jpg?v=1782529654\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19c-DSC_0106-600x379.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0876db254fd4134b.jpg?v=1782529657\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19d-wonderland-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d4ac610f46054669.jpg?v=1782529659\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19e-DSC_0111-600x434.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/39cccefce72dbdc2.jpg?v=1782529662\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19f-DSC_0113-600x399.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/50b5e9573c30f383.jpg?v=1782529665\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19g-DSC_0122-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b4ef2f94fcf111fd.jpg?v=1782529668\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19h-DSC_0128-600x416.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6ee73d380ef3f428.jpg?v=1782529670\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19i-DSC_0130-600x396.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/366909408bd13907.jpg?v=1782529673\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>And no LA Photo Party event is complete without a few jumping photos.</p>"
